    <item>
      <title>母亲退位后，腓特烈十世国王将继承丹麦王位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/denmark-gets-king-frederik-x-as-queen-margrethe-abdicates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，丹麦将见证近 900 年来的首次退位，届时女王玛格丽特二世将让位给她的儿子，即腓特烈十世国王。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/denmark-gets-king-frederik-x-as-queen-margrethe-abdicates</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜发射 2024 年第一枚疑似弹道导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/north-korea-fires-suspected-ballistic-missile-its-first-of-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜周日发射了一枚疑似弹道导弹，这是 2024 年首次发射此类导弹，领导人金正恩承诺增强该国的核打击能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/north-korea-fires-suspected-ballistic-missile-its-first-of-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 06:44:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>门口的农民领导反抗奥拉夫·肖尔茨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/angry-german-farmers-agrarians-at-the-gate-lead-the-revolt-against-scholz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一凌晨 5 点，辛西娅·弗雷 (Cynthia Frey) 将爬上她的 300 马力拖拉机，穿过黑暗前往柏林市中心。在那里，她将与其他数百名农民一起在勃兰登堡门呼吁总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/angry-german-farmers-agrarians-at-the-gate-lead-the-revolt-against-scholz</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾谴责中国在民主选举问题上的“疯狂谬论”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/taiwan-condemns-china-s-wild-fallacy-over-democratic-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在北京批评民主投票后，台湾抨击中国声称台湾选举是习近平主席政府的内政的说法是荒谬的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/taiwan-condemns-china-s-wild-fallacy-over-democratic-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 04:17:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁比尔·阿克曼支持迪恩·菲利普斯挑战拜登</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/billionaire-ackman-backs-democrat-phillips-to-challenge-biden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁比尔·阿克曼 (Bill Ackman) 表示，他将捐款 100 万美元，支持明尼苏达州众议员迪恩·菲利普斯 (Dean Phillips) 成为 2024 年总统选举的民主党候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/billionaire-ackman-backs-democrat-phillips-to-challenge-biden</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 03:38:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德桑蒂斯寻求在爱荷华州党团会议前几天平息捐助者的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/desantis-seeks-to-quell-donor-worries-days-ahead-of-iowa-caucus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佛罗里达州州长罗恩·德桑蒂斯的总统竞选活动试图向捐助者保证，他在爱荷华州的行动足以动员选民，尽管新的民意调查显示他失去了支持，而且寒冷的气温可能会降低党团投票率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/desantis-seeks-to-quell-donor-worries-days-ahead-of-iowa-caucus</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 03:19:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>党团会议前几天，爱荷华州民意调查显示，特朗普以 48% 的支持率领先黑莉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/trump-leads-with-48-in-iowa-poll-two-days-before-caucus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)以48%的支持率参加爱荷华州预选，一项备受关注的民意调查显示，尼基·黑利(Nikki Haley)以20%的支持率跃居第二位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/trump-leads-with-48-in-iowa-poll-two-days-before-caucus</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 02:08:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>停摆迫近之际，众议院和参议院正在研究权宜之计的资金协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/house-senate-working-on-stopgap-funding-deal-as-shutdown-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国会领导人正在制定一项新的权宜之计支出协议，以使联邦政府的资金持续到 3 月份，从而有可能避免 1 月 20 日开始的政府关门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/house-senate-working-on-stopgap-funding-deal-as-shutdown-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 00:42:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普转向拉马斯瓦米，告诉爱荷华州人“不要被骗”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/trump-turns-on-ramaswamy-telling-iowans-don-t-get-duped</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普将目光投向了竞争对手维韦克·拉马斯瓦米，将他视为“让美国再次伟大”运动的威胁，这似乎是爱荷华州预选会议前两天战略的转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/trump-turns-on-ramaswamy-telling-iowans-don-t-get-duped</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 23:51:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称投票后美国不支持台独</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/biden-says-us-does-not-support-taiwan-s-independence-after-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，在台湾选民反抗中国并回归执政的民进党之后，美国不支持台湾独立。它试图限制北京的影响力——至连续第三个任期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/biden-says-us-does-not-support-taiwan-s-independence-after-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 15:50:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
